version_description: Need that A in the main riff and the D variations in the bridge.
Transposed down 2 steps from original version added capo on 2nd fret to make it more acoustic friendly. Also added and changed the chords at the end of each chorus.
This is the only acoustic chords version of this song on the site, all else are electric tabs.
These chords fit well with the album version.
